metadata.title: I Fought The Law Fraction 1
metadata.description: A fractionalized Banksy (British, b.1974) I Fought the Law, 2004 Screen print printed in colours, signed and dated in pencil lower right, numbered 11/150, published by Pictures on Walls, London, with their blindstamp, on wove paper with full margins. Accompanied by a certificate of authenticity issued by Pest Control Office within each fraction.
